      "content": "it's just all so pointless. i look at my life and there is literally nothing there. no purpose, no future, just this constant, heavy exhaustion. it feels like the only logical thing for someone in my position to do is just... stop. like, why keep fighting a battle that was already lost? it would be so much easier to just let go.",
